| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3541 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9eeff6c5-6fd9-5c1d-ad5c-55e607de787d"
